{"id":682,"parent_id":680,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":682,"title":"Ecclesiastes 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Eccl.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","All the riches and wealth of the king are vanity and vexation of spirit—Wisdom is better than folly—God gives wisdom, knowledge, and joy to man."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.1","order":"02.22.002.44152"},["b","1"],"I said in mine heart, Go to now, I will prove thee with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"mirth"],", therefore enjoy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"pleasure"],": and, behold, this also",["i","is"],"vanity."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.2","order":"02.22.002.44153"},["b","2"],"I said of laughter,",["i","It is"],"mad: and of mirth, What doeth it?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.3","order":"02.22.002.44154"},["b","3"],"I sought in mine heart to give myself unto wine, yet acquainting mine heart with wisdom; and to lay hold on folly, till I might see what",["i","was"],"that good for the sons of men, which they should do under the heaven all the days of their life."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.4","order":"02.22.002.44155"},["b","4"],"I made me great works; I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"builded"],"me houses; I planted me vineyards:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.5","order":"02.22.002.44156"},["b","5"],"I made me gardens and orchards, and I planted trees in them of all",["i","kind of"],"fruits:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.6","order":"02.22.002.44157"},["b","6"],"I made me pools of water, to water therewith the wood that bringeth forth trees:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.7","order":"02.22.002.44158"},["b","7"],"I got",["i","me"],"servants and maidens, and had servants born in my house; also I had great possessions of great and small cattle above all that were in Jerusalem before me:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.8","order":"02.22.002.44159"},["b","8"],"I gathered me also silver and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"gold"],", and the peculiar treasure of kings and of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"provinces"],": I gat me men singers and women singers, and the delights of the sons of men,",["i","as"],"musical instruments, and that of all sorts."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.9","order":"02.22.002.44160"},["b","9"],"So I was great, and increased more than all that were before me in Jerusalem: also my wisdom remained with me."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.10","order":"02.22.002.44161"},["b","10"],"And whatsoever mine eyes desired I kept not from them, I withheld not my heart from any joy; for my heart rejoiced in all my labour: and this was my portion of all my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"labour"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.11","order":"02.22.002.44162"},["b","11"],"Then I looked on all the works that my hands had wrought, and on the labour that I had laboured to do: and, behold, all",["i","was"],"vanity and vexation of spirit, and",["i","there was"],"no profit under the sun."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.12","order":"02.22.002.44163"},["b","12"],"¶And I turned myself to behold wisdom, and madness, and folly: for what",["i","can"],"the man",["i","do"],"that cometh after the king?",["i","even"],"that which hath been already done."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.13","order":"02.22.002.44164"},["b","13"],"Then I saw that wisdom excelleth folly, as far as light excelleth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"darkness"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.14","order":"02.22.002.44165"},["b","14"],"The wise man’s eyes",["i","are"],"in his head; but the fool walketh in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"darkness"],": and I myself perceived also that one",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"event"],"happeneth to them all."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.15","order":"02.22.002.44166"},["b","15"],"Then said I in my heart, As it happeneth to the fool, so it happeneth even to me; and why was I then more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"wise"],"? Then I said in my heart, that this also",["i","is"],"vanity."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.16","order":"02.22.002.44167"},["b","16"],"For",["i","there is"],"no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"remembrance"],"of the wise more than of the fool for ever; seeing that which now",["i","is"],"in the days to come shall all be forgotten. And how",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"dieth"],"the wise",["i","man?"],"as the fool."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.17","order":"02.22.002.44168"},["b","17"],"Therefore I hated life; because the work that is wrought under the sun",["i","is"],"grievous unto me: for all",["i","is"],"vanity and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"vexation"],"of spirit."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.18","order":"02.22.002.44169"},["b","18"],"¶Yea, I hated all my labour which I had taken under the sun: because I should leave it unto the man that shall be after me."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.19","order":"02.22.002.44170"},["b","19"],"And who knoweth whether he shall be a wise",["i","man"],"or a fool? yet shall he have rule over all my labour wherein I have laboured, and wherein I have shewed myself wise under the sun. This",["i","is"],"also vanity."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.20","order":"02.22.002.44171"},["b","20"],"Therefore I went about to cause my heart to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"despair"],"of all the labour which I took under the sun."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.21","order":"02.22.002.44172"},["b","21"],"For there is a man whose labour",["i","is"],"in wisdom, and in knowledge, and in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"equity"],"; yet to a man that hath not laboured therein shall he leave it",["i","for"],"his portion. This also",["i","is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"vanity"],"and a great evil."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.22","order":"02.22.002.44173"},["b","22"],"For what hath man of all his labour, and of the vexation of his heart, wherein he hath laboured under the sun?"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.23","order":"02.22.002.44174"},["b","23"],"For all his days",["i","are"],"sorrows, and his travail grief; yea, his heart taketh not rest in the night. This is also vanity."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.24","order":"02.22.002.44175"},["b","24"],"¶",["i","There is"],"nothing better for a man,",["i","than"],"that he should eat and drink, and",["i","that"],"he should make his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"soul"],"enjoy good in his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"labour"],". This also I saw, that it",["i","was"],"from the hand of God."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.25","order":"02.22.002.44176"},["b","25"],"For who can eat, or who else can hasten",["i","hereunto,"],"more than I?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.26","order":"02.22.002.44177"},["b","26"],"For",["i","God"],"giveth to a man that",["i","is"],"good in his sight wisdom, and knowledge, and joy: but to the sinner he giveth travail, to gather and to heap up, that he may give to",["i","him that is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"good"],"before God. This also",["i","is"],"vanity and vexation of spirit."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.1a","order":"02.22.002.44178"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/14.13"},"Prov. 14:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.121"},"D&C 88:121"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.1b","order":"02.22.002.44180"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pleasure"},"TG Pleasure"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/selfishness"},"Selfishness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.4a","order":"02.22.002.44182"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/7.1.1-12"},"1 Kgs. 7:1 (1–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.8a","order":"02.22.002.44184"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/9.28"},"1 Kgs. 9:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/10.10.10-14"},"10:10 (10–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.8b","order":"02.22.002.44186"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/20.14"},"1 Kgs. 20:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.10a","order":"02.22.002.44188"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/3.22"},"Eccl. 3:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/5.18"},"5:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.9"},"9:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.13a","order":"02.22.002.44190"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/darkness-spiritual"},"TG Darkness, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.14a","order":"02.22.002.44192"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/17.24"},"Prov. 17:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.14b","order":"02.22.002.44194"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.2"},"Eccl. 9:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.15a","order":"02.22.002.44196"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/6.11"},"Eccl. 6:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.16a","order":"02.22.002.44198"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/3.19"},"Eccl. 3:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.16b","order":"02.22.002.44200"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/49.10"},"Ps. 49:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.17a","order":"02.22.002.44202"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/1.14"},"Eccl. 1:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.20a","order":"02.22.002.44204"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/despair"},"TG Despair"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.21a","order":"02.22.002.44206"},["b","21a"],["span.small","OR"],"propriety, skill."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.21b","order":"02.22.002.44208"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vanity"},"TG Vanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.24a","order":"02.22.002.44210"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/12.19.19-21"},"Luke 12:19 (19–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.24b","order":"02.22.002.44212"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/labor"},"TG Labor"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.26a","order":"02.22.002.44214"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/13.22"},"Prov. 13:22"],"."]]}
